      "totalPages": 20,
      "pages": [
        {
          "page": 1,
          "zh": "他们是一群看起来很奇怪的动物，聚集在岸边。",
          "enRich": "{g|They} were indeed {g|a queer-looking party} that {b|assembled} on {g|the bank}."
        },
        {
          "page": 2,
          "zh": "他们都湿透了，想办法把自己弄干。",
          "enRich": "{g|They} were all {g|wet}, and {b|wanted} to {b|get} dry."
        },
        {
          "page": 3,
          "zh": "老鼠说：安静！我要给你们讲一个干燥的故事。",
          "enRich": "{g|The Mouse} {b|said}: Silence! {g|I} will {b|tell} {g|you} {g|a dry story}."
        },
        {
          "page": 4,
          "zh": "老鼠讲了威廉征服者的历史。",
          "enRich": "{g|The Mouse} {b|spoke} about {g|William the Conqueror}."
        },
        {
          "page": 5,
          "zh": "但大家还是湿的。",
          "enRich": "But {g|everyone} was still {g|wet}."
        },
        {
          "page": 6,
          "zh": "渡渡鸟说：最好的办法是开一场会议赛跑。",
          "enRich": "{g|The Dodo} {b|said}: {g|The best thing} to {b|get} {g|us} dry would be {g|a Caucus-race}."
        },
        {
          "page": 7,
          "zh": "什么是会议赛跑？爱丽丝问。",
          "enRich": "What {b|is} {g|a Caucus-race}? {b|asked} {g|Alice}."
        },
        {
          "page": 8,
          "zh": "渡渡鸟在地上画了一个圆圈。",
          "enRich": "{g|The Dodo} {b|marked} out {g|a course} in {g|a sort of circle} on {g|the ground}."
        },
        {
          "page": 9,
          "zh": "大家随便站好。",
          "enRich": "{g|Everyone} {b|stood} in places here and there."
        },
        {
          "page": 10,
          "zh": "渡渡鸟喊：开始！",
          "enRich": "{g|The Dodo} {b|called} out: {b|Start}!"
        },
        {
          "page": 11,
          "zh": "他们乱跑了半个小时。",
          "enRich": "{g|They} {b|ran} about for {g|half an hour}."
        },
        {
          "page": 12,
          "zh": "渡渡鸟喊：比赛结束了！大家都赢了！",
          "enRich": "{g|The Dodo} {b|called}: {g|The race} is over! {g|Everybody} has {b|won}!"
        },
        {
          "page": 13,
          "zh": "现在发奖品。",
          "enRich": "Now for {g|the prizes}."
        },
        {
          "page": 14,
          "zh": "爱丽丝拿出糖果给大家。",
          "enRich": "{g|Alice} {b|handed} out {g|comfits} to {g|everyone}."
        },
        {
          "page": 15,
          "zh": "爱丽丝也需要奖品。",
          "enRich": "{g|Alice} must have {g|a prize} too."
        },
        {
          "page": 16,
          "zh": "爱丽丝从口袋里拿出顶针。",
          "enRich": "{g|Alice} {b|found} {g|a thimble} in {g|her pocket}."
        },
        {
          "page": 17,
          "zh": "渡渡鸟把顶针作为奖品给了爱丽丝。",
          "enRich": "{g|The Dodo} {b|presented} {g|the thimble} to {g|Alice} as {g|her prize}."
        },
        {
          "page": 18,
          "zh": "老鼠说：我的故事又长又悲伤。",
          "enRich": "{g|Mine} is {g|a long} and {g|sad tale}, {b|said} {g|the Mouse}."
        },
        {
